{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"757051a6ec","title":"关于国防部恢复炮击命令的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3f55f1b107","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":20,"articleId":"757051a6ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"fc7c1928d0","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在周思来1958年10月20日12时半关于警告美舰在金门海域护航的新闻稿和国防部恢复炮击金门的命令发布问题的报告上的两个批语。周思来的报告说：“警告美国在金门海域护航的新闻已于今日十二时半起广播，连续二次，中外文相同。新闻稿附后。国防部命令稿已写好，现送上请批阅后即退我，再以打字稿分送邓、陈、黄三同志核阅。厦门前线，切准备好了，已分别以电话和文字命令下达，由克诚签发，并告以炮击只限于金门各岛的工事、阵地和滩头船只，不打民村、兵房和指挥机关，更不要误击美国船只，我空海军均不出动。国防部命令拟三时广播，以口头广播读完后，立即开炮，中外文语同时广播。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"2d830c65d9","type":"title","text":"关于国防部恢复炮击命令的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec"},{"id":"fc7c1928d0","type":"paragraph","text":"照办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec"},{"id":"9dfc725248","type":"paragraph","text":"毛口头广播后，隔一小时，或半小时，开始炮击，较为适宜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec"},{"id":"3fb4bcfc4c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec"},{"id":"ae14825e65","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十日下午一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec"}],"page":{"id":"de44cc4723","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"757051a6ec","start":323,"end":324}}}},"__N_SSG":true}